      <div type="edition" xml:lang="mi-Latn">
	<p>
	  <lb n="1"/>
	    mahābhoje maṃdave kochipute
	    <persName key="pers:Velīdatta">velīdate</persName>
	    <persName key="pers:Ahila">ahilasa</persName> putasa
	    adhagachakasa
	    <persName key="pers:Rāmadatta">rāmadatasa</persName>
	    deyadhama cetiyagharo uparako
	    ca bhayāva sa
	    <persName key="pers:Velīdattā">velīdatāva</persName>
	    deyadhaṃmaṃ uyarako
	</p>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  The meritorious gift of a caityagṛha and cell by
	  <persName key="pers:Rāmadatta">Rāmadatta</persName>
	  the Adhagacchaka, the son of
	  <persName key="pers:Ahila">Ahila</persName>,
	  when Kautsīputra 
	  <persName key="pers:Velīdatta">Velīdatta</persName>
	  was Mahābhoja Mandava, and by his wife
	  <persName key="pers:Velīdattā">Velīdattā</persName>
	  the meritorious gift of a cell.
	</p>
      </div>
